    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes extensions to the Bidirectional Forwarding Detection (BFD) protocol to measure BFD stability. Specifically, it describes a mechanism for detection of BFD frame loss, of delays in frame transmitter and receiver engines, and of inter-frame delays that might explain issues with a BFD session.</t>
